INSERT INTO aggregator.user_history
                SELECT
                    psoe.market_id,
                    psoe.order_id,
                    psoe."time",
                    NULL,
                    psoe.integrator,
                    0,
                    psoe.max_base * mre.lot_size,
                    'open',
                    'swap'
                FROM place_swap_order_events AS psoe
                INNER JOIN market_registration_events AS mre ON mre.market_id = psoe.market_id
                WHERE psoe.txn_version > $1
